ied itself with the pretense of keeping the world safe from dangerous weapons in the hands of dangerous governments.<\/p>\r\n<p><\/p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/policymic\" class=\"twitter-follow-button\" data-show-count=\"false\" data-size=\"large\">Follow @policymic<\/a><\/p>","VideoUrl":"","EmbedCode":"","AttributionText":"","AttributionLink":"","ApImageUrl":null,"Position":9,"Deleted":0,"CreatedAt":"2013-09-03 20:50:13","UpdatedAt":"2013-09-05 17:58:08"}]

